      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box aw-briefly\">\n\t\t\t國外投資人是蠻看好比亞迪的<br/>\n目前電動車的領頭羊是特斯拉<br/>\n緊隨其後的是比亞迪和其他的中國車廠<br/>\n德國車廠拼命追趕<br/>\n所以說比亞迪對國外來說是個威脅沒錯<br/>\n<br/>\n節錄華爾街日報《特斯拉和中国车企领跑电动车赛道，德国车企竭力追赶》<br/>\n<pre>追踪全球电动汽车销量EV-Volumes.com网站数据显示，<br/>\n大众汽车是去年全球第四大电池电动汽车制造商，市场份额为8%，低于上一年的10%。<br/>\n特斯拉稳坐市场领头羊的交椅，其次是比亚迪和上汽集团。</pre><br/>\n<br/>\n----------------------------<br/>\n根據EV-Volumes.com的內文（機翻）<br/>\n特斯拉和中國車型占據前十<br/>\n特斯拉推出了一款新的暢銷車型 Model Y，不僅在電動汽車領域，而且在該類別的所有 SUV 和跨界車中，包括內燃機車。 豐田漢蘭達、福特探險者、寶馬X3、奔馳GLC、比亞迪宋等家用品牌的全球年銷量通常為300-40萬輛。 2022 年，Model Y 的銷量達到 771,000 輛，遠遠超過同等尺寸和價格範圍內的任何其他內燃機汽車。 不過，由於特斯拉優先生產更受追捧、利潤更高的 Model Y，Model-3 受到了打擊。儘管如此，Model-3 去年的銷量首次超過了五菱迷你電動汽車。<br/>\n通用五菱的迷你電動汽車銷量停滯不前，因為它面臨著來自奇瑞QQ和其他超便宜迷你通勤車等類似概念車的更多競爭。<br/>\n比亞迪有6款車型進入全球前十，其中宋、秦、漢、唐成為全球最暢銷的四款插電式混合動力汽車； 這是比亞迪去年四月放棄的常規內燃機業務的遺產。 宋PHEV是一款車長470cm的中型SUV<br/>\n圖片：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZXYtdm9sdW1lcy5jb20vd3AtY29udGVudC91cGxvYWRzLzIwMjMvMDIvV1ctTi0xMi0yMDIyLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.ev-volumes.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/WW-N-12-2022.png\">https://www.ev-volumes.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/WW-N-12-2022.png</a><br/>\n<pre>Top-10 Dominated by Tesla and Chinese Models<br/>\nTesla has a new best-seller, the Model Y, not only in the EV sector, <br/>\nbut within all SUVs and Cross-Overs in this category, including ICEs. <br/>\nHousehold nameplates like the Toyota Highlander, Ford Explorer, <br/>\nBMW X3, Mercedes GLC, BYD Song, etc. <br/>\nusually sell 300-400 000 units per year globally. <br/>\nThe Model Y reached 771 000 units in 2022, <br/>\nfar more than any other ICE vehicle in this size and price bracket. <br/>\nThe Model-3 took a beating, though, <br/>\nas Tesla prioritized production of the more sought after and more <br/>\nprofitable Model Y. Still, the Model-3 outsold the Wuling Mini-EV last year <br/>\nfor the first time.<br/>\nGM-Wuling's Mini EV sales stagnated as it faces more competition from similar <br/>\nconcepts like the Chery QQ and other ultra-cheap mini commuters.<br/>\nBYD had 6 models in the global top-10, with the Song, Qin, Han and <br/>\nTang as the world's four best selling PHEVs; a legacy from their regular <br/>\nICE business which BYD abandoned in April last year. <br/>\nThe Song PHEV is a mid-size SUV of 470cm length / 168cm height, <br/>\nthe starting price was 153 000 RMB in 2022, less than half of a Tesla Model Y. <br/>\nThere is a Song BEV variant with 71 kWh battery capacity for 180 000 RMB, <br/>\nwhich sold 67 000 units in 2022. The newcomers Dolphin and Yuan Plus had <br/>\na flying start and are exported in larger numbers now.<br/>\nThe VW ID.4 is the best selling model from a European brand. Sales include <br/>\nthe ID.4 X and ID.4 Crozz made by VW's joint ventures with SAIC and FAW in China.</pre> <div class=\"aw-stretch-content-button-container\"><button class=\"aw-stretch-content-button\" type=\"button\"></button></div></div>",
